<p>The Wolvercote Road section of the estate has been identified as a priority site to come forward in the Councilâ€™s <a href="https://www.bexley.gov.uk/sites/bexley-cms/files/2017-11/London-Borough-of-Bexley-DIFS-Higher-Growth-Report.pdf">Local Plan</a> but a planning application is yet to come forward.</p>

<p>Bexleyâ€™s <a href="https://www.bexley.gov.uk/sites/default/files/2018-02/Bexley-Growth-Strategy.pdf">Growth Strategy</a> envisages 4,000 new homes in the Thamesmead area facilitated by the new Crossrail station and including the â€˜renewalâ€™ of existing estates.</p>

